<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; background: #f4f4f9; padding: 50px; text-align: center; }
        .card { background: white; padding: 30px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
        h1 { color: #333; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="card">
        <h1><%= title %> 🛒</h1>
        <p>Day 1 is a wrap! Your Express ESM server is running beautifully.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>